Tell us how you sit front row and which wedding dress is your favorite!

node.text:
Welcome back inside my design studio for the making of a collection. The Hayley Paige Spring 2019 collection is about confidence, not compromise; exploring empowerment principles and how energy is truly a universal language. Each bridal gown in this collection represents a different value in the same way a superhero manifests a special skill; everything from loyalty and resilience to grit and gratitude is in attendance. This is for the bride that values love, loyalty, and laughter … "she's gotta go see about a gown.” Styles Shown:
